               <msContents>
                  <summary>I) Maṣḥafa gǝnzat “Book of the Funeral Ritual” (fols. 3ra-112vb)
 -
                     Introduction (fols. 3ra-7va)
 - Discourse of St Athanasius on death (fols.
                     7va-12ra)
 - Maṣḥaf za-wäḍʾat ʾǝm-ʾIyarusalem “Book that Came from
                     Jerusalem” (fols. 12ra-17va)
 - Antiphons (kǝśtat) (fols. 30ra-30vb,
                     46vb-47ra, 71va-vb, 73va-vb, 77va-78ra, 82va)
 - Homily by St Jacob of
                     Serug for the funeral of priests and deacons (fols. 53rb-59va)
 - Homily by
                     ʾabbā Salāmā, Metropolitan of Ethiopia (fols. 59vb-62rb)
 - Lǝfāfa ṣǝdq
                     “Bandlet of Righteousness” (fols. 108arb-110ra)
 - Mangada samāy “Journey
                     to Heaven” (fols. 110ra-111va)
 
 Additiones 1-2.</summary>
