                     Besides, the names of Wälätä Gabrǝʾel (e.g., 3va),
                     Gabra Ṣādǝq (e.g., 17vb), Walatta Madḫǝn (e.g.,
                        22rb), Gabra Dǝngǝl (e.g., 26rb), Za-Walda Māryām (e.g., 39rb), Walatta Yoḥannǝs (e.g., 47va),
                     Tasfā Mikāʾel (e.g., 47vb) are written over
